In a large saucepan, combine SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and water. Boil for 5 minutes. Remove from heat, and add cinnamon sticks, allspice berries, cloves, and ginger. Cover, and let stand for 1 hour. Strain liquid into a large pot. Pour in orange juice, lemon juice, and apple juice; bring to boil. Remove from heat, and serve.